AboutUs.title: About Us
AboutUs.OurMission1: Our mission is as simple as it is powerful.
AboutUs.OurMission2: We want to allow citizens from all over the world to support, in a easy and fast way, social projects through their daily consumption. Thankyooh, moreover, also allows organizations to support its own social project, and to ask for the support of people throughout the world.
